1 business listed as a source of income as required under ORS 244.060 (3).
2 (4) “Candidate” means an individual for whom a declaration of candidacy, nominating petition
3 or certificate of nomination to public office has been filed or whose name is printed on a ballot or
4 is expected to be or has been presented, with the individual’s consent, for nomination or election to
